<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

  <div class="space-y-8 text-secondary">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-primary mb-3">How Your Data is Processed</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">When you use Fact Check, your audio is processed as follows:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-2 text-tertiary">
        <li>Audio is streamed to Deepgram for real-time transcription</li>
        <li>Transcribed text is sent to xAI (Grok) for claim extraction and fact-checking</li>
        <li>Results are displayed in your browser</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">By default, your session data is not stored permanently. However:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-2 text-tertiary">
        <li>If you enable recording (REC button), transcripts and fact checks are saved for developer analysis</li>
        <li>No raw audio is ever stored</li>
        <li>IP addresses are hashed for rate limiting only</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">This app uses the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-2 text-tertiary">
        <li><a href="https://deepgram.com/privacy" class="text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-colors underline decoration-border-medium" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deepgram</a> - Speech-to-text transcription</li>
        <li><a href="https://x.ai/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-colors underline decoration-border-medium" target="_blank" rel="noopener">xAI</a> - Claim extraction and fact-checking</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-primary mb-3">No Cookies or Tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-tertiary leading-relaxed">
        We do not use analytics cookies or tracking pixels. The only cookie stored is an encrypted session identifier.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10">
    <%= link_to root_path, class: "text-tertiary hover:text-secondary transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1" do %>
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18" />
      </svg>
      Back
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
